OOC: It should be noted that if they turn traitor again, then I will be 
forced to try and kill any characters belonging to Orchid that ever come near 
their base.

::Aerotaur/Aquataur::
       Aquataur gets up and runs around after Trinity very slowly.  She 
finally puts on a short burst of speed.  "Tag."  She puts a hand on Trinity's 
shoulder.  "You're it."

       Aerotaur nods to Nightlight.  "I stopped liking strangers who come to 
'join us' after the second or third group turned traitor and tried to kill 
us.  Well, we should go meet them anyway."  He sighs and walks out the door 
to meet the newcomers.

--part1_108.8146f9d.291a0672_boundary
